After building, share these to the recipient:
1. The built app:
dist/gcsheet/browser/   (entire folder - contains index.html + all JS/CSS)
2. If using PocketBase backend:
- Download PocketBase from https://pocketbase.io
- Share pocketbase.exe (or create a batch file to run it)
3. Optional - setup batch file:
Create a start.bat like your gcsheet.bat:
@echo off
cd /d "%~dp0"
pocketbase serve
start index.html